Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, housemate Mercy, on Friday night made a revelation about her love life before the reality show. Mercy, while discussing with fellow housemate, Elozonam, revealed that she was dating former Super Eagles striker, Emmanuel Emenike before he got married to ex-beauty Queen Iheoma Nnadi. She disclosed that she found out about his marriage to ex-beauty queen on Instagram while they were still dating. According to her, the footballer she claimed used and dumped her because she was a “nobody” at that time Mercy added that the situation at that time made her determined to become successful and be a celebrity. Meanwhile, Emenike is yet to respond to the allegation. VIDEO: Mercy telling Elo Emenike dumped her for former MBGN & she found out on instablog😭 Saying she’s determined to be a Celebrity as she feels he dumped her cos she had no social status#BBNaija pic.twitter.com/MdeO93PwGr — Pastor Clinton😇 (@Pastor_CVB) September 14, 2019  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.